summary: East Wing of Lakeview as an upgraded armory
descriptionHtml:
While trying to make a new west wing I decided to first do the entry and east wing. This is the east wing armory, i will load my entry when i figure out why half my shields aren't working. I was influenced by Lakeview Armory redone by [b]jecoil cause I really liked how he set up the mannequins and extra displays. 

10 Mannequins (7 on cabinets)
13 Cabinets (7 with mannequins)
1  Table
4  Large Display cases ([b]none of the displays are weapon specific)[/b]
4  Small Display cases (not specific dagger displays)
6  Single weapon plaques
11 Weapon/ shield plaques
16 Weapon racks
4  Chests (1 long & 3 little)

Build the East Armory Wing, But no interior furnature

if there are problems let me know... and i will put up pics when i figure out how to take them... or someone is nice and sends me some :D


[/b]
author: CavBirdie
